<sect1 id='gimp-imagewindow-menus-view'
  xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" lang="en;de;fr;zh_CN">
  <title lang="en">View</title>
  <title lang='de'>Ansicht</title>
  <title lang="fr">Affichage</title>
  <title lang="zh_CN">查看</title>

  <indexterm lang='en'>
    <primary>Image menu</primary>
    <secondary>View</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang='de'>
    <primary>Bildmenü</primary>
    <secondary>Ansicht</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang='fr'>
    <primary>Image menu affichage</primary>
  </indexterm>
  <indexterm lang='zh_CN'>
    <primary>图像菜单/查看</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <informalfigure lang="en;de;zh_CN">
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject>
        <imagedata
          fileref='../images/menus/menus-view.png'
          format="PNG"/>
       </imageobject>
     <caption>
       <para lang='en'>
         Contents of the View menu
      </para>
      <para lang='de'>
        Die Inhalte des Ansicht Menüs.
      </para>
      <para lang="zh_CN">
         查看菜单内容
      </para>
    </caption>
     </mediaobject>
  </informalfigure>
  <informalfigure lang="fr">
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject>
        <imagedata
          fileref='../images/menus/fr/menus-view.png'
          format="PNG"/>
       </imageobject>
     </mediaobject>
     <caption>
       <para lang='fr'>
         Contenu de menu Affichage
      </para>
    </caption>
  </informalfigure>

  <para lang='en'>
    The View menu contains commands that affect the visibility or
    appearance of the image and various elements of the interface.
  </para>
  <para lang='de'>
    Das Ansichtenmenü enthält alle Funktionen die dem verändern der
    Bildansicht dienen.
  </para>
  <para lang='fr'>
    Le menu Affichage contient les commandes qui affectent la 
    visibilité et l'apparence de l'image et des éléments de
    l'interface
  </para>
  <para lang="zh_CN">
    查看菜单包括影响图像可见性或外观以及界面不同元素的操作。
  </para>



